OL,5, A DNA test has revealed a dying man who
OL,6, claimed to be one of Japan's most      
OL,7, wanted criminals was telling the truth.
OL,9,FSatoshi Kirishima made his confession  
OL,10,Fin January, telling police "I want to  
OL,11,Fmeet my death with my real name".      
OL,13,FOfficials have now confirmed the       
OL,14,F70-year-old was indeed Kirishima, a    
OL,15,Fmember of a militant group behind      
OL,16,Fseveral deadly bombings in the 1970s.  
OL,18,FExactly how he remained at large for so
OL,19,Flong - despite his face adorning       
OL,20,Fposters across Japan - is unclear.     
